name: 凯伦·沃迪奇
introduction: Karen was born in Detroit, Michigan. Her Mother died when she was age 4 and her father remarried, so in addition to her 4 natural siblings she got 4 more in the bargain, making for a rather crowded station wagon. After graduating from the University of Iowa as a Theatre Major she moved to Chicago where she has appeared in numerous theaters, including Writers' Theatre, The Goodman Theatre, Northlight, Chicago Shakespeare Theatre and many others.
family_member: 马修·詹斯Matthew Janes（夫）/本杰明·詹斯Benjamin Janes（子）
